  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This protocol was designed for testing the intraoperative use of the Dune device. This
      multicenter study will take place in Israel at 12 sites.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Use of the device will take place during a partial mastectomy procedure (lumpectomy).The
      patient will be randomized to enter the device or control arm.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
